('6197', '141', 'Heat oil in a small skillet over medium-high heat.'),
('6197', '142', 'Add ginger, green onions and chiles and cook, stirring frequently, until fragrant but not browned, about 1 minute. Stir in lime zest and fish sauce and cook for about 10 seconds more.'),
('6197', '143', 'Pour mixture over fish and wrap up parchment paper snugly to form a packet.Carefully transfer fish to rack in wok or skillet. Bring water to a simmer over medium heat, cover and steam until fish is just cooked through, 8 to 10 minutes. Carefully remove parchment packet from wok and transfer to a large plate.'),
